VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \bpthread_create\s*\(.*\);\s*.*\s*=.*shared_var
WHEN EXPR MISSING:mutex|lock|atomic|std::mutex|pthread_mutex|synchronized|volatile\s+std::atomic
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects potential race conditions in multi-threaded applications.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Race Condition with Shared Resource.
